Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you want to become a scary king,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)あなたが なんで\N怖い王様になろうとするのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 私は あなたのことを…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how I feel about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you with whatever\Nyou're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:19.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが抱えているものを\N一緒に背負いたい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たっだいま～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-You idiot!\N-Say what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:44.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)こんな時間まで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where have you been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:48.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこ ほっつき歩いてんだ！\Nごめ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)あなた まさか\N竜になったんじゃないでしょうね？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't turn into a dragon, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ？\Nそ… そんなわけないじゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Well, I'm off to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 もう寝ま～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふっ｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)怪しいですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is acting fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)まったく\Nアフロは何をしてたのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world was Afro doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふふっ｡\N≫(ﾌｧﾊﾞﾛ･ﾚｵｰﾈ)ニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:17.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ あっ なんだ 師匠か｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚かさないでよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't startle me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～｡ 厄介な男に\Nほれちまったみてぇだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you fell for a guy who's real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:29.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nシャリオスに会ってたんだろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You met with Charioce, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何言ってんの 師匠｡\Nそんなわけ ないない！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Master?\NOf course I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:39.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん｡ そっか そうだよな➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:44.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前みたいなちんちくりんに\N王様が引っ掛かるわけねぇよなぁ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a little shrimp like you\Ncould hook a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そうだよ 師匠｡ んっ…\Nおっかしなこと言わないでよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪ぃ 悪ぃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)邪魔だ どけ｡\N(２人)ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:09.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお～ おめぇ\N朝から どこ行ってたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our group got a little bigger while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がいない間に\N仲間が増えたんだぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)\N俺は 貴様たちの仲間ではない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not part of your pathetic group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アザゼル よかった 無事で｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あのときは\N竜になれなくて ごめんなさい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I couldn't turn into a dragon\Nwhen you needed me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が あのとき…\Nあのとき 竜になっていれば…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd turned into a dragon then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)\N貴様が竜になろうと なるまいと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter whether\Nyou turn into a dragon or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ない｡\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から期待などしていなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected anything out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:05.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ アザゼル\Nムガロちゃんも戻ってきたんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugaro's back too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと\N前より成長しちゃってるけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit more grown up, but you should\Nstill be able to recognize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるでしょ？ って… あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Azazel recognize you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アザゼル 分かんなかったのかな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,RAGE OF BAHAMUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same\Nand lose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz there are lots of roads to go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the path suddenly seems rougher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna walk straight ahead\NKnock down another dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Most broke before they ever came true
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the way you think it\NTo a yielding heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the future, hope,\Ndespair and worry all look all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that you'll turn down the truth\Nthat lied to you that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were prepared for it all.\NYou go your way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)牢獄島の様子はどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the prison island look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching from the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)上空から見てましたけど\N近づく隙は なクワァったですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was no opening to get any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)街の方も\Nおめぇらが脱走したせいか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The city was full of soldiers, too,\Nmaybe in response to your escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵士だらけだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ～ 二人とも\Nちゃんと働いてたんだね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you two were actually working for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)遊んでたのは\Nあなたとアフロとアザゼルだけよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people who were playing around\Nwere you, Afro, and Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すいません｡\Nやはり 腕輪の情報が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the intel on the bracelet really our only lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一の手がかりか｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)そもそも 王様は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we even know if the king\Nalways has the bracelet on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その腕輪を\N常に着けているんですクワァね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕輪は\Nいつも着けているみたいだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he always has the bracelet on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで あなたが知ってるの？\Nえっ？ え～っと…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because I think he had it on\Nwhen I ran into him at the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前 牢獄で会ったときに\Nしてた気がしたから… あははっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:56.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが本当だとしてもよ\N今 王様に近づくのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,how are we supposed to even get near the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理がねぇか？\N(ﾘﾀ)４日後➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a ball at the palace in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王宮で舞踏会が開かれるわ｡\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)本当か？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)貴族の元患者からの\N情報だから 確かよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from a former patient who's a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタって 貴族も診てたんだね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you treated nobles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat anybody as long as they pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お金しだいで 誰でも診るわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その舞踏会を狙って\N王に接近するか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we try to move in on the king at the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潜入するにしても\N協力者が必要ね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need help if we're\Ngoing to sneak into the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your former patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタの元患者は？\Nあれは三下貴族だから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from a third-rate family.\NNo way he's getting an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,招待されないわ｡\N三下かい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に任せてくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then who is going to be the one sneaking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:31.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 次は 誰が潜入するかね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！ よっと｡ 私が潜入して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sneak into the ball\Nand steal the bracelet from the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王様から腕輪を奪います！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？ どした？\Nとっても不安ね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)お嬢さんは\Nもっと 暴れ回る役目の方が…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better suited for the\Njobs where you can go wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だって｡ 私 もう\N好きなときに竜になれるんだから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. I've learned how to turn into a dragon\Nwhenever I want to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)うそをつくんじゃねぇ！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying. We're not playing around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:55.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遊びじゃねぇんだ｡\Nお前は出しゃばるな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ！\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)うわっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グルル…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)どうやら… ごほっ\Nうそじゃないみたいね｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like she wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきも カイザルの隣にいて\N平気だったし｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed she was fine being next to Kaisar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男にドキドキするのも\N治ったのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you no longer\Nget flustered around men?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グルル…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 今更？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい｡\N愛されることを知ったから…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I learned what it feels like to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(考古学者)ドロモスを\N完全な出力で起動するには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We need 30 percent more energy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ３０％のエネルギーが\N足りません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to activate Dromos at maximum output.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)すぐに完全にしろ｡\Nですが 陛下 作業者たちに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish the task, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Your Majesty, the workers need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上の負荷は…｡\N褒美は 十分に与えている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They are being generously compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…｡\Nやれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye yai yai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)陛下 私からも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May I give you my report as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報告をよろしいでしょうか｡\Nかまわん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)昨夜 赤い竜の目撃情報が｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We received word that the red dragon\Nwas spotted last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,堂々と アナティの上空を\N飛んでいたとのことです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it was brazenly flying over Anatae.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,茶番は やめろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ら漆黒兵➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Onyx Soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての命は 王であるあなたに\Nささげております｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,offer our lives to serve Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give us the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか 使命の遂行に専念を｡\N分かっている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The red dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:17.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)赤い竜は？\N(漆黒兵)行方は まだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not located it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず現れる｡ もう間もなくな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It will appear without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The man we've discussed will arrive tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(漆黒兵)\N例の男は 今晩 到着いたします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quick. Have the money ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早いな｡ 金を用意しておけ｡\N(漆黒兵)御意｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)あっ あの… どうも｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと いいですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not tolerate Charioce's arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(兵士)おい 何をしている！\N(男性)あっ｡ おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey!\N-Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おう｡\N(兵士)待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捜せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)((包帯悪魔と呼ばれる\N賞金首は 俺だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the bounty being called the rag demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間どもをおとしめ\N魔族の失った誇りを取り戻す｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will slay the king of man and\Ntake back the pride the demons have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い竜を使う))\N(ﾀﾞﾝﾃ)((俺たちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use the red dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:07.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を ただ信じるしかない))\N(ﾍﾞﾙﾌｪｺﾞｰﾙ)((アザゼル様➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel, what is it that you are looking upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を見ておられるのですか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)((未来だ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(ｴﾙ)ごめんなさい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき\N助けられなくて ごめんなさい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I wasn't able to help you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も俺に謝るのか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're apologizing to me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)\Nお前が謝ることなど 何もない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,RAGE OF BAHAMUT
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in. Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾎﾞｰｲ)こちらです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to be making that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)いつまで\Nそんな顔してるんですか？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we come here every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毎晩 来てるわけじゃないんだし\Nいいじゃないですか｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:10.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厳しい訓練と任務に励んでるのに\N俺たちにゃ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We devote ourselves to our hard training and duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we not allowed any simple pleasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,娯楽も許されないんですか？\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)そんなわけではない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)だったらいいでしょ｡\Nさっ 早く座って｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)\Nだが こんな姿を団長が見たら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the captain saw us like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nはあ!? 見れるわけないでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How the hell would he do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ] ♬～(店内BGM)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アレサンド？\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)見れるわけないでしょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alessand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he won't see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人は今 脱獄中ですよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too busy being a wanted fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)どうも～！\N今日も元気なケルちゃんだぞ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cerby is here to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ワン｣｡ ｢ワン｣｡\Nおお～ ケル子➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cerby, I've missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会いたかったぜ｡\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)もう～ アレ君➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 来ないから\Nケル子は お怒りだぞ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm mad at you\Nfor not coming by at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガウガウ｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ごめん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾗﾐｱ)さっ 難しい顔してないで\N楽しみましょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how about you try to relax and enjoy yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ツンツンって… どう？\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)ガウガウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you okay, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)あら～ アレ君 大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)((あっ あの… どうも))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ちょっと いいですか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あの… 俺…))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((用があるなら 早く言え))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((お… 俺\N漆黒兵部隊に入りたいんです))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to join the Onyx Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あっ 待ってください！))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((本気なんです｡ ｵﾙﾚｱﾝ騎士団じゃ\Nもうダメなんです))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Orleans Knights are done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((価値がない))\N((えっ？ 価値？))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((貴様には\N隊に入れるほどの価値はない))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not worth adding to our squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)あっ アレ君\N彼 今日から入った新人君だよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his first day with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか お前 むかつく顔してんな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a real annoying face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:09.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい？\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)｢はい？｣じゃねぇよ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me?\N-No, don't "excuse me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta stop it with that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 その顔やめろよ！\Nおい！ うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろって言ってんだろ！\Nはい？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-I told you to stop.\N-Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちっ！\Nバキッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(女性たち)きゃあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)何をする アレサンド｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Alessand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:47.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？ なっ なんで…｡\Nうぐぐっ…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！\Nガシャン！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you here in disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)なぜ\N変装などして このような場所に？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)お前たちに会いたかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you must have known\Nthat we frequent places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)我々が\Nこのような店に通っていたことを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご存じだったのですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は お前たちの上司だぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力してほしいことがある｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like your help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私にできることなら なんなりと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アレサンド\Nお前にも協力してほしい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alessand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like your help as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of the weapon\NHis Majesty used, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:30.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちも 陛下が使用した\N破壊兵器は知っているだろう？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陛下が あの力で\Nこれ以上の争いを望むのなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If His Majesty wishes to use its power\Nfor further conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would like to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は それを止めたい｡\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)しかし どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The palace ball that will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)３日後に王宮で開かれる\N舞踏会 そこに潜入する｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will infiltrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで アレサンド➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is where, Alessand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の力を借りたいのだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)舞踏会には\N一部の貴族しか参加できない｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Only select nobles may attend the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名家である\Nヴィスポンティ家のお前なら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Being from the great Visponti family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that should be no trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,容易にできるだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む 力を貸してくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alessand.\N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)アレサンド｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)嫌ですよ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-I said, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)なんだ？\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)嫌だって言ったんですよ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで俺が そんなことに\N協力しなきゃいけないんですか｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to help you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:14.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 自覚あるんすか？\N反逆者で脱獄犯で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what your situation is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a traitor, a fugitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一級犯罪者なんすよ｡\Nそんなヤツのお願い➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the kingdom's most-wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do any favors for someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が聞くんすか！\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)アレサンド！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alessand.\N-And you're no better, Dias.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ﾃﾞｨｱｽさんもﾃﾞｨｱｽさんですよ\Nなんで いつまでも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-How can you keep licking his boots?\N-Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな人に へこへこしてんすか！\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)お前！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)俺たち この人のせいで\N惨めな目に遭ってんのに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He ruined our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで怒んないんすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:34.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまなかった｡\N今更 謝られたって遅いんすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちオルレアン騎士団が\N失ったものは もう戻らない｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Orleans Knights can never\Nget back what we've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:43.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは 価値のない人間に\N成り下がったんだ！ あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been reduced to being worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:48.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)お前たちは\N価値のない人間ではない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my prized subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の自慢の部下だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いのは 全て私だ｡ だが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully to blame for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回だけは\N協力してほしい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something I desperately need your help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ\Nこの命を失おうとも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I should lose my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 陛下の真意を\N知りたいのだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I must know His Majesty's intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)頼む｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ～ 言っときますけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危ないことはしないですからね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ!? ちょっと…｡\Nふふふっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Dias?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんすか ディアスさん｡\Nちょっと やめてくださいよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気持ち悪い！\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)何をてれてんだ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're grossing me out.\N-What are you blushing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいじゃないか｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)てれてないっすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きだ～～‼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫好きだ～～！\Nクワッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさいですねぇ｡\N≫好～き～だ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はははっ 言っちゃった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, my goodness, I said it.\N-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫何してんだ？ お前｡\Nし… 師匠！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Master? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see what all this commotion was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が騒いでるから\N何事かと思って 来たんだっつぅの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:43.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べ… 別に 何もないから\Nもう戻ってよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, so you can go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ 誰からもらった？\Nあっ これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ！ 見ないでよ エッチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look, pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エッチって お前…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ ニーナ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が\N何を隠しててもかまわねぇが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you think hard before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えて選択しろよ｡\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is put together pretty carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中ってのは\Nよく出来ててよぉ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを選ぶと 何かを失っちまう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you choose one thing,\Nyou lose something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:18.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 俺は\Nめんどくせぇそれを避けるために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to avoid all the nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由気ままに\N賞金稼ぎをしていたが…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and live my life as a bounty hunter,\Nfree to do what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then, there are times when\Nyou have to make important decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも 大事な選択を\Nしなきゃならねぇときは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:29.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来ちまうんだ｡\N師匠？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:34.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も その選択が正しかったのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make the right decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には分かんなくてな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:44.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前は\N後悔しねぇように しっかり選べ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you need to decide well,\Nso you don't have any regrets later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく分かんないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオスが好きなんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You love Charioce, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言えない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きだ～～‼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっ… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠 やめろよ！\Nはいはい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きだ～～‼\Nだあっ！ ほんと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:15.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,や～め～ろ～よ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きだ 好きだ！\Nうるさい うるさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shut up! Shut up!\N-Stop! Seriously! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:22.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！ マジ やめろ！ 危ねっ｡\N落ちろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Watch it! Come on!\N-I'm pushing you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫やめろ！\Nほんとに うるさいですねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ぐおぉ～…｡\Nクワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As horrible as you are\NI can't help but love you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while I waited\NThat is all I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:22:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ephemeral lovers, both flawed and missing pieces\NWe have finally become one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in this miniature garden at the edge of sorrow\NCan you hear my heart speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I may no longer feel\Nthat I want to go back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are feelings, feelings, feelings\NI can only feel now
